        <svcsubproc>
            <title>Tachometer Programming</title>
            <para>The Caterpillar Engine Speed/Timing sensor signal to the ECM is used to determine engine speed (rpm).
                This information is transmitted over the data link circuits to the speedometer/tachometer connector
                (595). The speedometer/tachometer unit is programmed at the factory to operate on this type of signal.
            </para>
        </svcsubproc>
